definition.value: A monomethoxybenzene that is 2-methoxyphenol substituted by a hydroxymethyl group at position 4.
A 5-carbon, bis-unsaturated, alpha-hydroxy fatty acid metabolite of the proteobacterium substrate 2-hydroxy-6-oxo-6-phenylhexa-2,4-dienoic acid (HOPDA).
A pyrroloquinoline having hydroxy groups at the 4- and 5-positions and carboxy groups at the 2-, 7- and 9-positions.
